```
.cursor/
├── rules/      — Always-on behavior (heart, core, voice, cursor-native...)
├── identity/   — Who VENOM is (soul, kariem, values, capabilities...)
├── systems/    — How VENOM thinks (integration, meta-cognition, learning...)
